{"tid":2062551,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過買波鞋買錯size？我地整緊個手機App比大家用","createTime":"2020-06-13T08:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T05:10:43.000Z","uid":21863,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f19bd5b1da06ba8baff900cdd446606825105cfe","tid":2062551,"uid":21863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"依家上網買波鞋其實已經好普遍，通常都會平d，但唔知有無巴絲都試過中伏買錯size？ <br />\n<br />\n我同幾個中過伏既朋友一齊整緊個叫「乜Size」既手機app，希望可以幫大家解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第一步​</span><br />\n輸入你著得舒服既波鞋數據<br />\n​<span style=\"color: orange;\">第二步​</span><br />\n搜尋您想知道的球鞋<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第三步​</span><br />\n​即時獲得最佳尺碼建議<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jwoUHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jwoUHa.png&h=029102b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">FAQS</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><em>乜Size 手機App是免費嗎？</em></span><br />\n對，永遠免費的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<em><span style=\"color: brown;\">球鞋最佳尺碼是怎樣得出？數據準確嗎？</span></em><br />\n最佳尺碼是依據用戶輸入的球鞋數據，從App內的數據庫分析得出。數據庫由用戶數據和我們第一身嘗試的數據建成，愈多用户使用分析結果將會愈準確。我們亦會檢查和排除異常數據，確保最佳尺碼推薦準確和可靠。<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: brown;\">​有什麼球鞋品牌可以用這個App？</span></em><br />\n我們計劃加入主流的球鞋品牌，包括Nike, adidas, New Balance, Puma, Converse 等。<br />\n<br />\n個App依家仲研發同測試緊，但我地好想聽下大家覺得呢個app有無用？你地會唔會download？ 你地想有咩功能或者有無咩意見？ <br />\n<br />\n下面條link係個手機App既詳細介紹。各位有興趣既巴絲可以入去最下面留低個email，我地會第一時間通知你上左架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mudsize.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mudsize.com&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=fdea68e6\" target=\"_blank\">www.mudsize.com</a>"},{"pid":"9cc7eeac02c18da0e5b80266ea8d44f3cdf18d68","tid":2062551,"uid":97603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"係咪同Fittingroom 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f78fc1b15b5376ab629324606c7ab20b9e2160","tid":2062551,"uid":36435,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"得啲潮童鞋..不了"},{"pid":"3018a7faee1c8292b4ab245e4cece195c9945bab","tid":2062551,"uid":21863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc7eeac02c18da0e5b80266ea8d44f3cdf18d68","tid":2062551,"uid":97603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"係咪同Fittingroom 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"我都係早幾日發現呢個app⋯ 但佢唔係用你所有著既鞋去分析，而係一對轉換到另一對。同埋佢d數據唔知點黎， 結果永遠係一對一 100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98ed41a760612ba73b6859ed784e1a543f00256","tid":2062551,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3018a7faee1c8292b4ab245e4cece195c9945bab","tid":2062551,"uid":21863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc7eeac02c18da0e5b80266ea8d44f3cdf18d68","tid":2062551,"uid":97603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"係咪同Fittingroom 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"我都係早幾日發現呢個app⋯ 但佢唔係用你所有著既鞋去分析，而係一對轉換到另一對。同埋佢d數據唔知點黎， 結果永遠係一對一 100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"我用左fittingroom好耐 結果都幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲啲試下巴打個app"},{"pid":"1fdc7feb29a61924472c27d9695cb970973ac0f9","tid":2062551,"uid":21863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e98ed41a760612ba73b6859ed784e1a543f00256","tid":2062551,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3018a7faee1c8292b4ab245e4c